# Secure mode: Education (EU/IE)

This pack adds GDPR-aligned student privacy workflows plus the Irish Data Protection Commission’s “Children’s Fundamentals”. It is opt-in and keeps classic templates untouched.

## Getting started

```bash
speckit compliance plan --framework edu-eu-ie
speckit compliance verify --framework edu-eu-ie
```

- `plan` writes working docs to `docs/internal/compliance/edu-eu-ie/**`, including the GDPR checklist and DPC fundamentals.
- `verify` inspects `edu-eu-ie-controls.yaml`, enforces the age-of-digital-consent guardrail, and writes `.speckit/compliance-report.(json|md)`.

