| `edu-eu-ie-controls.yaml` | Evidence tracker for objective checks |

## Age of digital consent

Ireland defaults to age {{ edu_eu_ie.config.age_of_digital_consent }} for digital consent under GDPR Article 8. To support another Member State, edit `.speckit/spec.yaml`:

```yaml
compliance:
  enabled: true
  frameworks:
    - id: edu-eu-ie
      config:
        member_state: "fr"
        age_of_digital_consent: 15
```

Re-run `speckit compliance plan --framework edu-eu-ie` to refresh docs after updating the config. Templates cite GDPR Article 8 and the DPC guidance automatically using your configured age.

